imdb.plot outline: The "Eye on You" Television Show was created for people who believe that our youth are our future, and as such should be allowed to discuss current events and issues affecting our communities. This unique television show offers an opportunity for middle school, high school, and college students from all over the country to guest star on television with high-profile politicians and other community leaders.
imdb.title: Illegal Immigration Part II
